{"tid":1479834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"817光復紅土前夕","createTime":"2019-08-17T05:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T06:17:49.000Z","uid":291448,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cde1c3b389e6c03697765cdb5e2b2713d81c2f4f","tid":1479834,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NvDvRqP5zbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNvDvRqP5zbU&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=fbafd4fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NvDvRqP5zbU</a><br />\n<br />\n尋日行過大陸旅遊團經常出沒嘅地點 幾乎一架旅遊巴都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原本諗住以為D大陸旅遊團應該呢排唔會再落嚟紅磡土瓜灣呢一帶啦 行下行下點知呢 係返屋企嘅途中比我見到有一團大陸旅遊團喺土瓜灣食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過總括黎講呢排紅土一帶算係平靜左小小咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係紅磡土瓜灣係唔應該有旅遊團出沒 即使有少少都唔容許！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為呢度唔係啲咩旅遊區 只係普通住宅區黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以作為紅土人今日一定要出嚟光復紅土！不見不散！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5f52ec1d7596c4064f83e3891691651345daf92e","tid":1479834,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"光復紅土 還我淨土"},{"pid":"d53108b715b8baf617e3c3f98f8fb112fbe1b305","tid":1479834,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"海心公園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48dc9b2b5265eeaa5c5d7eb6c07b818839b8d64a","tid":1479834,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復紅土"},{"pid":"40eb352b10669f5895105976091ccbc7c9ed2c87","tid":1479834,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"以前住土瓜灣 嘈撚到仆街<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"831b0072391beecf55377d1edcb69613587e09f1","tid":1479834,"uid":79401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"一陣見！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復紅土！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLqYzLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLqYzLE.jpg&h=4e7df2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DegQqSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDegQqSj.jpg&h=e8f20d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RSoLSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RSoLSj.jpg&h=69c7f50c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZ33LSk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZ33LSk.jpg&h=9840d73e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e728c5360d2d2359e43b21f4ce3bd98eb0223384","tid":1479834,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"今朝紅蘋果啲檔口好多都收晒無開ON99<br />\n3點半先開波"},{"pid":"57c01c57508fd86bd4ea399b01f56d34f76bc3f8","tid":1479834,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e728c5360d2d2359e43b21f4ce3bd98eb0223384","tid":1479834,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"今朝紅蘋果啲檔口好多都收晒無開ON99<br />\n3點半先開波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"嗰班低學歷嘅街市佬以為會行到去紅蘋果<